Privacy Policy

Welcome to WhisperWave! We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and share information when you use our app and services.

1. Information We Collect
We collect information you provide directly, such as account details and content you post. Additionally, we collect data automatically, including your usage patterns, IP address, browser type, and device information.

2. How We Use Your Information
We use your information to provide and personalize our services, display relevant ads, and ensure the safety of our platform. We may also recommend connections based on your interests and interactions within the app.

3. Sharing Your Information
Your information may be shared with other users, service providers, and as required by law. In case of business transactions, such as mergers, we may transfer your information accordingly.

4. Advertising
We use AdMob to display personalized ads based on your interactions with our app and other apps. AdMobâ€™s privacy practices can be found in their Privacy Policy.

5. User Responsibilities
Users are responsible for the content they post. We do not tolerate illegal activities or harmful behavior and may take action against violations, including content removal and account suspension.

6. Your Choices
You can manage your account settings, cookie preferences, and ad choices through the controls available in the app.

7. Data Security
We implement security measures, including encryption, to protect your data from unauthorized access and misuse.

8. Changes to This Policy
We may update this policy periodically. Significant changes will be communicated through updates to this page. We encourage you to review this policy regularly.

9. Copyright Protection
We do not allow any content that infringes copyright. Unauthorized use of copyrighted content may lead to content removal, account suspension, or termination.

10. Trademark Protection
We respect trademark rights and take measures to prevent consumer confusion about the products or services offered by different entities. Any reported violations will be addressed promptly.

11. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at whisperwave25@gmail.com.

Effective Date
This Privacy Policy is effective as of 21 July 2024.
